# FlipCard Specification

## Required Props

title: string

## Optional Props

image (front photo), backImage (back photo), description (front only), backItems (back bullets only), badge, link, ctaLabel

## Front vs Back

- Front: `image` + title + description in bottom-left label panel with scoop corner
- Back: optional `backImage` (full bleed) OR solid `backColor` (default white); `backItems` bullet list + optional CTA on content layer

## Behavior Props

revealMode: 'click' | 'hover' | 'tap' | 'scroll'
flipDirection: 'horizontal' | 'vertical'
animationStyle: 'smooth' | 'snappy' | 'dramatic'
mobileBehavior: 'tap' | 'scroll' | 'disabled'
autoFlip?: boolean, autoFlipDelay?: number

## Appearance Props

borderRadius, shadow, backColor, textColor, overlayColor, padding, frontPanelColor, frontTitleColor, frontDescriptionColor, panelScoopRadius

## Interaction Rules

- Desktop: hover or click
- Mobile: tap or optional scroll reveal
- Never rely exclusively on hover

## Scroll Reveal

Use IntersectionObserver or whileInView; expose threshold, once, staggerIndex

## Framer

Property controls live in `FlipCard.framer.tsx`. Deploy steps: `src/components/FlipCard/DEPLOY.md`.
